name: Test product 420
description:
The flexible basis for transportation solutions.

The Audi genuine carrier units offer many options to increase the transportation possibilities of you vehicle. Quick and simple mounting of bicycle racks, ski and snowboard holders as well as kayak racks. Materials used such as support feet, cover caps and trims are made from ageing-resistant plastic, mechanical parts are made from high-quality coated sheet steel. The carrier units are equipped with an anti-theft locking system and have been city crash tested.

Limitations:

  • For vehicles without roof rails

Information:

For vehicles with roof rails. High-quality materials. Simple fitting. Sporty, slender design with Audi Logos. Specially developed for the respective model. Carrier profile with T-groove for easy securing of attachments



Suitable for:

Audi Q4 e-tron
  • Audi Q4 e-tron Sportback 2021 >

General information: Maximum usable upper width of carrier: 970 mm
Remarks: City Crash tested
Remarks: The maximum permissible total weight of 75kg for the bars, mounted parts and load must not be exceeded
Own weight [kg]: 5
Colour: Silver/black
Contents: 1 set = 2 items (front and rear carrier bars)
Contents: With theft-inhibiting locking mechanism (coded clamping screw). Including aero-acoustically optimised profile cover and detailed installation instructions.
Support type: Rail rack
Support section: T-slot
